How A Supermodel Got Destroyed By A Cult: Ruslana Korshunova

She had the looks, the fame, the life. Ruslana Korshunova lit up catwalks and Vogue covers, then plunged to her death from a Manhattan balcony. No note. No warning. Just a beautiful girl, gone at 20. Behind the glamour? A secretive group that promised healing but acted like a cult. This is how a supermodel got pulled in… and never came out.
